Rate limiting app:

Tools and techs:
Spring Boot Application
Redis using Redisson java client 
RRateLimiter implemented by Redisson


how to run:
docker-compose build
docker-compose up

Then you can interact with the API (example: curl http://localhost:8080/hello)

callouts:
The rate limiting is done in filtering but the same functionality can be integrated into any API
No tests yet, didn't had much time, sorry about that.


